snippet.title: Noble's Life: Kingdom Reborn Playtests Teaser
snippet.description:
We invite you to sign up for the first closed playtest of Noble's Life on Steam!

Signups start from 29.09.

See game before anyone else and give your opinion and find your ruling style!

Learn more and join Playtests on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1662050/Nobles_Life_Kingdom_Reborn/

Join us on Discord:
https://discord.gg/tpnzmQSXNh

Like us on Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/NoblesLife

Follow us on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/Nobles_Life
